<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>QCobro — Restablecer contraseña</title>
  <style>
    body { margin: 0; padding: 0; background-color: #f4f5f7; }
    .wrap { width: 100%; background-color: #f4f5f7; padding: 32px 0; }
    .card {
      max-width: 480px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      background: #ffffff;
      border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
      border-radius: 14px;
      padding: 32px;
      font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
      color: #111827;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }
    .button {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 12px 24px;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #047857 0%, #10b981 100%);
      color: #ffffff !important;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 8px;
      font-weight: bold;
    }
    .muted { color: #6b7280; font-size: 13px; }
    .hr { height: 1px; background: #eef0f2; border: 0; margin: 24px 0; }
    @media (prefers-color-scheme: dark) {
      body, .wrap { background-color: #0b0f0d !important; }
      .card { background: #14181a !important; border-color: #23292c !important; color: #e5e7eb !important; }
      .qcobro-name { color: #f8fafc !important; }
      .muted { color: #9ca3af !important; }
      .hr { background: #23292c !important; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="card">
      <table role="presentation" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0">
        <tr>
          <td style="width:38px;height:38px;background:#047857;border-radius:9px;text-align:center;vertical-align:middle;">
            <span style="color:#ffffff;font-size:21px;font-weight:800;font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;line-height:38px;">Q</span>
          </td>
          <td style="padding-left:10px;vertical-align:middle;">
            <div class="qcobro-name" style="font-size:18px;font-weight:800;color:#0f172a;letter-spacing:-0.3px;line-height:1.1;">QCobro</div>
            <div style="font-size:10px;font-weight:500;color:#64748b;letter-spacing:0.4px;line-height:1.4;">by Fonoster</div>
          </td>
        </tr>
      </table>

      <hr class="hr" />

      <p style="margin:0 0 12px;">Solicitaste restablecer la contraseña de tu cuenta de <b>QCobro</b>.</p>
      <p style="margin:0 0 20px;">Para crear una nueva contraseña, haz clic en el botón de abajo:</p>
      <p style="margin:0 0 8px;"><a href="{{resetPasswordUrl}}" class="button">Restablecer contraseña</a></p>
      <p class="muted" style="margin:16px 0 0;">Si no solicitaste este cambio, puedes ignorar este mensaje.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
